    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>游戏将在未来几周内，推出一个类似“自定义”模式，或者一个“编辑器”，用来完善任务时限、体力消耗、平衡性等方面的游戏机制。</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开发团队正全力修复部分玩家遇到的功能性BUG，发售的这10天内，已发布5个小型更新补丁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>后续的更新补丁仍在继续制作中！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果您遇到地图不显示任务的情况，现在可暂时通过“退出到主界面，再重新进入游戏”来解决这个问题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>十分感谢各位玩家的持续反馈，这对游戏未来发展有着至关重要的积极作用！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们设置了专门的客服来更高效的服务大家！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果您遇到卡死、卡顿或者其它问题，亦或是由游戏本身有任何建议。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢迎联系官方客服QQ2117308548进行反馈</strong>，我们会第一时间为您解答，并全力寻找解决方案。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812860/extras/37cbce6399ca2746df8943bcb9ee72f5.avif?t=1769684777\" alt=\"Dice Gambit\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812860/extras_big/37cbce6399ca2746df8943bcb9ee72f5.avif?t=1769684777 width=800 height=200 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812860/extras/5132ff545937eaf6a9383baaf8c514f9.poster.avif?t=1769684777\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=616 height=257 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812860/extras/5132ff545937eaf6a9383baaf8c514f9.webm?t=1769684777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>成为一名光荣的裁决使，带领你（债台高筑的）的家族扑杀城里猖獗肆虐的异色怪物。解锁独一无二的技能，结识古怪的贵族，探索城内的秘密，还能抽空帮人送送冰淇淋！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812860/extras/e967680b1ea31f7eac0d606e328854d4.poster.avif?t=1769684777\" width=616 height=401 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812860/extras/e967680b1ea31f7eac0d606e328854d4.webm?t=1769684777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >凭借天赐强运，带领一干骑士披荆斩棘</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >奇招百变，杀得敌人片甲不留</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >落子有悔，让你主宰自己的命运</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随机应变，机巧尽出，最终胜算在握</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812860/extras/953bfaa4fab6ecb3110052854d6e9c94.poster.avif?t=1769684777\" width=616 height=401 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812860/extras/953bfaa4fab6ecb3110052854d6e9c94.webm?t=1769684777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>200</strong>多种技能和被动效果由你挑选，构筑出千奇百怪的战术</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富的学院课程供你尽情摸索各色机制</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种职业随心搭配，打造你如臂使指的梦幻团队</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >纷繁的构筑和协同效果，让你在战场上只手遮天</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812860/extras/8aad6c2d3524b7ef95040ab484728843.poster.avif?t=1769684777\" width=616 height=401 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812860/extras/8aad6c2d3524b7ef95040ab484728843.webm?t=1769684777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开创万代基业，打造名门望族</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强强联姻，开枝散叶</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >培养子嗣，传承力量</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >见证你的家族日益壮大，重振裁决使的伟大辉煌</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812860/extras/f6451684c45add055e62214d7b7e9073.poster.avif?t=1769684777\" width=616 height=401 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812860/extras/f6451684c45add055e62214d7b7e9073.webm?t=1769684777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在新塔利斯城中结交达官贵人，左右逢源，牢牢攥住他们的把柄</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >借势乘运，登堂入室，攫取更加强大的技能</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对机遇切记谨慎挑拣，才能在新塔里斯城中开辟你自己的道路</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >飞黄腾达途中，谁将与你携手共进，抵掌相庆？</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
